  "description": {
    "zh": "很高兴你来了，雇佣兵。我刚想起来一件事：我那个朋友一直想去疗养院看看。他总说自己真的需要休假，但一直没时间。\n\n他还提到一个项目，一个很大的项目，一个能\"改变规则\"的项目。还要和某个重要人物会面。具体在哪，我不知道。你得去调查。",
    "en": "Glad you came by, mercenary. I have just remembered something: that friend of mine always wanted to visit the health resort. He kept saying he really needed a vacation, but he couldn't find the time.\n\nHe also mentioned a project, something big, something that would \"change the rules\". And a meeting with someone important. Where exactly, that I don't know. You'll have to investigate."
  },
